{"tid":2228674,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蘋果A1: 12港人扣內地　 喬映瑜被指組織偷渡　兄憂妹抑鬱病發亂認罪","createTime":"2020-10-03T18:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T08:40:48.000Z","uid":240362,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"f7f42ddcbadd82e44946fb8885172fa4017a1aa0","tid":2228674,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T18:31:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/120731164_10159502439667448_3920654296464421419_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=EIi_nSel2CQAX_isjpF&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;oh=4d11def8487692b8d28912ba20a3b636&amp;oe=5F9EFC1C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F120731164_10159502439667448_3920654296464421419_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DEIi_nSel2CQAX_isjpF%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26oh%3D4d11def8487692b8d28912ba20a3b636%26oe%3D5F9EFC1C&h=b1147e57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】被扣留在深圳逾一個月的12名港人日前被正式批准逮捕，被捕者中唯一女子、33歲的喬映瑜被指涉嫌組織他人偷越邊境罪，罪名較其他被捕者更重。喬映瑜胞兄打破沉默接受本報專訪，透露妹妹患有抑鬱症10年，擔心她在病情影響下誤認控罪，呼籲內地政府實踐「陽光司法」，勿將12港人當成政治籌碼。昔日兄妹情深，哥哥形容失去妹妹如失掉身上一塊肉。他請特區高官易地而處，考慮家屬的無助感受。<br />\n<br />\n他指映瑜是家中老么，與父母兄姊一家五口生活融洽，即使她早前離家自住，但每逢節日都會聚會慶祝，一家人不時燒烤、看電影。憶起往日與妹妹的相處情境，一個大男人亦幾度哽咽，重複說着「我唔見咗個妹，我真係好擔心」，形容這種錐心之痛「好似自己身上冇咗嚿肉咁」。他說上次見映瑜是1月的家人燒烤聚會，當時妹妹未見異樣，若然可以與妹妹再見一面，他希望表達家人的愛和支持：「我會話，只要你返嚟屋企，屋企人會全力幫你、撐你。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/LXM6Y3YHSVCF7HJ5COT66TPB7E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2FLXM6Y3YHSVCF7HJ5COT66TPB7E%2F&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdqVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=e9897221\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2FLXM6Y3YHSVCF7HJ5COT66TPB7E%2F&h=b5474304\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/LXM6Y3YHSVCF7HJ5COT66TPB7E/</a>"},{"pid":"81b14d9f312f1709fabbb33fdc6ece370bd44109","tid":2228674,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T18:32:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"595e87ee61a17b51ca02b535a506246193b79b23","tid":2228674,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81b14d9f312f1709fabbb33fdc6ece370bd44109","tid":2228674,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T18:32:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T18:33:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d442ad1b0a7d80115974b088a768046f8f355a","tid":2228674,"uid":111856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T18:33:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eff57f8db414d8070fd3b7e60647d92d247dd26","tid":2228674,"uid":103965,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T18:34:10.000Z","msg":"屌真係有機會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />重度抑鬱又無藥食真係會癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44067e8b3909f540403b35c15754859feae79179","tid":2228674,"uid":378793,"like":3,"dislike":53,"score":-50,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T18:34:30.000Z","msg":"應該俾公安玩爛咗下面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下世唔好咁蠢想救呢班垃圾香港人"},{"pid":"1b79619d4f5